description: Total Full and Part-time Jobs in Maryland and its Jurisdictions (by Place of Work) by Type and Industry from 2005 to 2010. The data also includes total number of jobs and total number wage and salary by state and jurisdictions. Source from the U.S. BEA Table CA-25N, May 2012. The estimates of employment for 2005-2006 are based on 2002 (NAICS). The estimates for 2007 forward are based on the 2007 NAICS.
